     * +-----+--------+----------+-------+-------+-/-+-------+-------+--------+
     * |flags|entry-id|num-fields|field-1|value-1|...|field-N|value-N|lp-count|
     * +-----+--------+----------+-------+-------+-/-+-------+-------+--------+
